      "id": "PopularPost17460",
      "post_content": "@ Elysiume, I think you are missing the point of this card. Your complaint is like saying [Banefire](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Banefire) is a bad card because if you play it on turn 1 with a single mountain it does 0 damage.   \n  \nCards like this take finesse and timing that something simple like an efficant but basic card like Savanna lion does not require.  \n  \nSadly the only one of these I could pick up at the local game store was in japanese but it's a rad card for heavy discard deck, and the art is top notch.",
      "posted_by": "yojimbojones",
